<style>
.widget-contact {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0 20px 40px;
  background: url(/images/bg-office.jpg) no-repeat 50% 50%;
  background-size: cover;
  color: #fff;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .widget-contact {
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
}
.widget-contact .bg {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
}
.widget-contact .bg:after {
  opacity: 0.9;
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  background-color: var(--color-footer-background);
}
.widget-contact .bg video {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.calculator {
  position: relative;
  padding: 60px 0;
}
.calculator-heading {
  margin-bottom: 35px;
  text-align: center;
}
.calculator-heading h3 {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.calculator-heading small {
  display: block;
  opacity: 0.7;
  margin-top: 5px;
  font-size: 12px;
}
.calculator-form {
  position: relative;
}
.calculator-form + .calculator-form {
  margin-top: 20px;
}
.calculator-form label {
  display: block;
}
.calculator-form input {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 50px;
  line-height: 50px;
  margin-top: 10px;
  padding: 0 40px 0 0;
  border: none;
  background-color: rgba(35, 44, 58, 0.8);
  box-sizing: border-box;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 16px;
  text-align: right;
}
.calculator-form input:focus {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  outline: none;
}
.calculator-form sub {
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  padding-right: 20px;
  line-height: 50px;
}
.contact-card {
  display: block;
  position: relative;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  background-color: var(--color-mobile-nav-background);
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.contact-card + .contact-card {
  margin-top: 15px;
}
.contact-card:hover {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}
.contact-card h3 {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.contact-card h3 i,
.contact-card h3 img {
  position: absolute;
  top: 15px;
  right: 15px;
  font-size: 30px;
}
.contact-card p {
  margin-top: 12px;
  line-height: 22px;
}
</style>

<div class="widget-contact">
  <div class="bg">
    <video autoplay loop muted playsinline>
      <source src="/videos/bg-meeting.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
  </div>
  <div class="calculator">
    <div class="calculator-heading">
      <h3>감정평가 수수료 계산</h3>
      <small>국토교통부 공고 제 2016-1220호</small>
    </div>
    <div class="calculator-form">
      <label>
        예상 감정평가액을 입력해주세요.
        <input type="tel">
        <sub>원</sub>
      </label>
    </div>
    <div class="calculator-form">
      <label>
        예상 수수료 (VAT/실비 별도)
        <input type="tel" disabled>
        <sub>원</sub>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="contact-card" href="tel:<%= config.tel %>">
    <h3>
      <i class="fa fa-id-card"></i>
      전화 상담
    </h3>
    <p>
      <%= config.author %><br>
      <u><%= config.tel %></u>
    </p>
    <p>빠르고 간편하게 상담이 가능합니다.</p>
  </a>
  <a class="contact-card" href="<%= config.kakao %>" target="_blank">
    <h3>
      <img src="/images/ui-contact-kakao.png" width="35" height="35">
      카톡 상담
    </h3>
    <p>
      1:1 채팅을 통해<br>
      상담 및 예약을 도와드립니다.
    </p>
  </a>
</div>